{"type": "article", "id": 24532, "title": "3D打印“花瓶”", "description": "", "date": "2016-03-28T06:04:39Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 161922, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 24, "image": "img/article/article_show/201606061608435UandijhlBmFXT1A.jpeg", "contents": "\n\n<p class=\"\">将塑料瓶废物利用做成花瓶并不新鲜，但往往也没什么美观。米兰的设计师 Libero Rutilo 的设计重点在于瓶子外的黑色的“壳”，他做了 4 种 3D 打印的网状的壳，有的像钻石的纹路，有的是蜘蛛网格，还有的模拟了陶瓷花瓶的流畅曲线，罩在盛满水的塑料瓶外面就像真的有一个玻璃花瓶一样。一点简单的改变就可以让生活有趣味。<a href=\"http://www.designlibero.com/portfolio/3d-printed-vases-collection/\">点击这里可以查看更多信息。</a><br></p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-active medium-insert-images-wide\">\n<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201606061608415w4ZxIzBXEC0lqA6.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"medium-insert-image-active\" data-ratio=\"0.755\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"medium-insert-caption-placeholder\"></figcaption></figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160606160841WfBiQp16TzaJqnsM.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.89166667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160606160842h1b9rpLu5I2sFUT8.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.5\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160606160842sZunm51NUR0MjTHb.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.5\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n\n\n"}